{"tid":804961,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 網瘋傳男女高中生在樓梯間打砲 啪啪啪15秒就結束了...","createTime":"2018-09-03T12:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T12:34:51.000Z","uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0923a6e3db2a75439088ee110d1d8c4e8cc66711","tid":804961,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕網路論壇「Dcard」近來有用戶PO文，透露自己在8月30日下班時在樓梯間聽到奇怪的聲響，一探頭赫然看到兩個高中生在打砲，而男學生果然血氣方剛，啪啪啪15秒就射了，讓女孩忍不住嬌嗔「怎麼那麼快？」<br />\n<br />\n從網路流傳的影片可以看到，男女學生站在樓梯間，先是傳來幾次呻吟，接著男方掀起女學生的裙子，以「四腳獸」背後式的姿勢往前突刺，啪啪啪的聲音與女孩的嬌喘交融在一起，但10幾秒就戛然而止，男學生離開女孩臀部開始整理褲子，女高中生此時嗔道：「你射了喔？怎麼那麼快？」<br />\n<br />\n網友們看到影片後開始瘋狂討論，不少人認為從影片裡男女學生的制服上看來，似乎是台北市的兩所學校，還有人透露這是在補習班的樓梯間，其他網友則直呼女孩「聲音好甜喔」、「聲音聽了好酥麻」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpRWv0gJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpRWv0gJ.jpg&h=601a9334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2539338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2539338&d=%2F1J9eyi%2FGVE8pPY2j%2BbW77%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c7c21c46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2539338&h=5872a939\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2539338</a>"},{"pid":"520ac15546f99b526ad6035c70ffd927825701d8","tid":804961,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"仲衰過吳彥祖"},{"pid":"a087d5071f04fb146348f02ee23d1a0e7a2c545a","tid":804961,"uid":34841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"太多圖 爆埋data"},{"pid":"0273168e4cc0596b451eddaece890002bca1c3b0","tid":804961,"uid":119610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"網路流傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor